text: The Tiinle (, ) is a Somali clan which is also subclan of darod clan they live in kaladhac town near Waiye district and Af Ururhttp://www.abtirsi.com/view.php?person=10244&abtirsiLang;=6http://allsanaag.com/ugaaska- tiinle-oo-sheegay-inuu-xadka-soo-xirayo/. They are fathered with Gabtaanle, Dishiishe and Maganlabe. ==References== Category:Ethnic groups in Somalia
